---
title: Messy Indian-Style Chicken Thigh Flatbreads with Green Peppers and Tikka Sauce
description: Enjoy all the flavours of chicken tikka masala in flatbread form! Toasted flatbreads are smothered in warm, buttery tikka sauce, then topped with tender chicken, crunchy green peppers and tangy feta cheese. These balanced flatbreads are finished with cilantro for a touch of brightness.
